#dnat DNS to Maxima Telecom Proxy DNS
dnat in proto udp to port eq 53 redir to 194.85.154.158 port 53
dnat out proto udp from 194.85.154.158 port eq 53
dnat in proto tcp to port eq 53 redir to 194.85.154.158 port 53
dnat out proto tcp from 194.85.154.158 port eq 53
# dnat HTTP
dnat in proto tcp to port eq 80 redir to 194.67.1.40 port 18080
dnat out proto tcp from 194.67.1.40 port eq 18080
# dnat HTTPS
dnat in proto tcp to port eq 443 redir to 194.67.1.40 port 18443
dnat out proto tcp from 194.67.1.40 port eq 18443
# everything else should be blocked 
block in
block out
